title: Walking In The Fullness Of His Blessing | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Walking In The Fullness Of His Blessing | Joel Osteen
description:
What God has done in the past is only a glimpse of what He's going to do in the future. Because you're His child, He's lining things up in your favor. Now do your part and get in agreement. You still haven't seen all that He has prepared for you!


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
